[02:06] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'multiple references now you can actually use your trained characters. So on this slot, I\'m going to click it and choose character and I\'m going to select Helena here, the AI version. And in the prompt,'

[02:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'I\'m going to prompt for placing the small pop can in the hand of the woman with black hair, identifying the object and where the object\'s going in regards to the subject. And if you want to keep'

[02:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the consistency of your character, it\'s always good practice to prompt maintain the exact face, likeness, and outfit or something very similar. And we see that this time around the pop can is actually'

[02:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'a decent size. One of her fingers is probably hidden behind the pop can there. So I did another one that had all her fingers. But you see all the details of her outfit is consistent throughout.'

