AUDIO: 'And here\'s the easy part. You can either generate a brand new image of two different characters as long as they\'re full view, meaning head to toe, or you can train a character either with a'

[05:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'description, one image, or four plus images. Helena and I have done videos on these methods. I encourage you to check them out. And whether you use one image or the character, all you need to do is'

[05:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'click on character. Here\'s my character Ruby. And if you look at her shoulders, even the little waist material there, that\'s sort of like a belt, the straps'

[05:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
